

	 
      The night was closing in fast, the birds had long since stopped making their cheerful clatter of a noise, instead all you could hear was the long slow moans of the grasshoppers, hoping from one piece of grass to another, it was rather soothing to listen to them, all alone in the dead of the night.  “For God’s sake mark will you open this fucking door up!” came the loud angry shout from the human we call Danny, “Its going down tonight, we need you there, now open up this fucking God damn door!” “Alright, alright, calm down you’ll wake the neighbours” the quiet voice of Mark could be heard saying “What fucking neighbours?” Danny shouted as he continued banging his fists on the door, “you live in the fucking countryside!” 
     

    
